  "detailed_description": "<strong>You are the governor of a new island. Build and manage your own colony. </strong><br>This is a fantasy city-building strategy game with focus on production chains and settlers desires.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529830/extras/6d27c074490d78d4c745b13eab8f73a5.poster.avif?t=1762735794\" width=300 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529830/extras/6d27c074490d78d4c745b13eab8f73a5.webm?t=1762735794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529830/extras/6d27c074490d78d4c745b13eab8f73a5.mp4?t=1762735794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Citizens are primary resource. </strong><br>Gather and process resources and maintain the needs of your colonists.<br>To keep them happy, you can provide them with luxuries, variant foods, medicines, services, and more.<br>Can you lead the city without citizens being unhappy and sick?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529830/extras/d7e586e90f0cc699a756502aad15d4c9.poster.avif?t=1762735794\" width=300 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529830/extras/d7e586e90f0cc699a756502aad15d4c9.webm?t=1762735794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529830/extras/d7e586e90f0cc699a756502aad15d4c9.mp4?t=1762735794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Establish numerous production chains, and use adjacency bonus for more prosperity.</strong><br>You can get resources by simple processing at first.<br>But you'll need to build complex production chains to get advanced resources.<br>The island is small, and there are obstacles and useful natural objects.<br>Use the space efficiently!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529830/extras/59d29564e0e9bbf87bd9a80b226fb628.poster.avif?t=1762735794\" width=300 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529830/extras/59d29564e0e9bbf87bd9a80b226fb628.webm?t=1762735794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529830/extras/59d29564e0e9bbf87bd9a80b226fb628.mp4?t=1762735794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Research technologies, and unlock new knowledge and resources.</strong><br>You can develop freely your city with 25 types of research and 54 types of buildings.",
