ces.<br>The island is small, and there are obstacles and useful natural objects.<br>Use the space efficiently!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529830/extras/59d29564e0e9bbf87bd9a80b226fb628.poster.avif?t=1762735794\" width=300 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529830/extras/59d29564e0e9bbf87bd9a80b226fb628.webm?t=1762735794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529830/extras/59d29564e0e9bbf87bd9a80b226fb628.mp4?t=1762735794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Research technologies, and unlock new knowledge and resources.</strong><br>You can develop freely your city with 25 types of research and 54 types of buildings.",
